Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.04,0:00:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子的爹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.55,0:00:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.65,0:00:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.36,0:00:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.86,0:00:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的，怎么又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.26,0:00:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子的爹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.07,0:00:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,吵死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.18,0:00:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,爱理，你去说说他们啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.89,0:00:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.19,0:01:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竞他是我爸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.10,0:01:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我去有点尴尬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.04,0:01:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.67,0:02:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,爽啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.57,0:02:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,老公...不要停
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.48,0:02:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,用力...用力干我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.88,0:02:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这样对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.08,0:02:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,真爽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.88,0:02:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,真的好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.80,0:02:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,来...来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.12,0:03:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,老公...老公...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.82,0:03:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不要停嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.92,0:03:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.03,0:03:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不要停下来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.55,0:03:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,（每晚都与母亲做爱的老爸 受不了诱惑的老婆）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.45,0:03:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,(趁着危险日爬上老爸的床)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.73,0:05:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,等我\N快...快点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.44,0:05:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,等我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.24,0:05:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,到了...到家了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.04,0:05:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你很努力了，真的\N累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.95,0:05:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,爱理，打扫辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我们去洗个澡，然后就吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.86,0:05:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧\N嗯 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.28,0:05:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么没水
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.28,0:05:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.38,0:05:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,出来了...水出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.49,0:05:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不要在这里弄啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.49,0:05:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,来，水温还可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.59,0:06:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌啦，老公真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.20,0:06:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,看到你就这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.80,0:06:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌，你好坏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.71,0:06:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,昨晚真的好吵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.42,0:06:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,年纪都那么大了 收敛一点好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.73,0:06:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.83,0:06:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟你爸感情好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.03,0:06:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你们两个的感情还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.44,0:06:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,也该生小孩了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.14,0:06:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,对了，你们结婚4年还是5年了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.74,0:06:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,老伴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.15,0:06:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是你换工作之后自己说要跟我们住的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.65,0:07:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,如果那么在意 你们到外面租房子住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.46,0:07:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你爸身体那么好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.56,0:07:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,还不需要你们勉强跟我们一起住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.56,0:07:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,老伴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.32,0:08:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.53,0:08:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉，我软掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.24,0:08:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了 好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.84,0:08:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子的爹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.56,0:08:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.77,0:09:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.48,0:09:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.78,0:09:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子的爹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.70,0:09:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,老公，你真的好猛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.61,0:09:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,跟夏子在一起 我还可以再来2次3次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.21,0:09:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌，你还能再来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.21,0:09:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我好幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.71,0:09:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你摸摸看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.62,0:09:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.82,0:09:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.22,0:09:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我还想要\N先帮我弄硬点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.04,0:10:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,应该一下子就硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.44,0:10:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,厉害，真的硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.54,0:10:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,对，就这么弄
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.04,0:10:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,变得好硬\N再弄硬点... 对,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.15,0:10:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,这样弄吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.85,0:10:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,真好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.46,0:10:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我也好想尝试这种激烈的性爱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.07,0:10:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,硬了吧\N真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.28,0:10:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,真的好硬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.38,0:10:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,很想要了吧\N好想要哦 孩子的爹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.68,0:10:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那你骑上来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.09,0:10:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,真的可以吗\N可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.16,0:10:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.01,0:11:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.74,0:11:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,老公，你好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.04,0:11:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,千死你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.38,0:12:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.78,0:12:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,用力....用力...对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.59,0:12:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.01,0:12:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,对，就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.25,0:13:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这样弄好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.46,0:13:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒，看得好清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.67,0:13:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,一览无遗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.38,0:14:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服...好爽...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.08,0:14:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.58,0:14:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,很爽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.39,0:14:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,真的要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.20,0:14:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,爽死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.50,0:14:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不要停嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.71,0:14:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.81,0:14:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不要拔出来，就这么干 对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.83,0:14:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.73,0:15:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,老公好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.65,0:15:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢这么...我喜欢这么...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.06,0:15:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,老公，我最喜欢你这么干我了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.76,0:15:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.89,0:15:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,爽\N很爽吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.89,0:15:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,真的好爽哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.69,0:16:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,爽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.40,0:16:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你动作快一点\N快点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.20,0:16:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,对对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.70,0:16:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,爽，要去了...又要去了 让我升天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.41,0:16:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,太美妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.11,0:16:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.01,0:16:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,又去了啊\N老公你真能干
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.32,0:16:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,又去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.32,0:16:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.33,0:16:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,从后面...从后面干我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.83,0:16:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你转过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.44,0:16:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你趴好来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.44,0:16:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,快来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.65,0:16:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,要来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.65,0:17:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,快，快从后面干死我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.37,0:17:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这样很爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.68,0:17:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,真爽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.29,0:17:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,骚货
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.39,0:17:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,腰自己扭起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.80,0:17:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,真爽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.31,0:17:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌，不要停嘛，用力地干出声音来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.61,0:17:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.83,0:18:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,真的好有感觉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.94,0:18:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,要...要去了...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.75,0:18:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,爽死我了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.75,0:18:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,真的好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.96,0:18:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,越来越有感觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.56,0:18:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,爽吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.96,0:18:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.67,0:19:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,过来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.00,0:19:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,爽...真的好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.71,0:19:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,老公好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.22,0:19:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我也好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.13,0:19:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,爽啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.14,0:20:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,真爽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.94,0:20:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,爽吧，爽死你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.15,0:20:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,爽...要爽死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.90,0:21:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,妈，你要出门吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.21,0:21:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我预约了要去护肤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.31,0:21:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,难怪皮肤这么好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.81,0:21:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,真开心，谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.41,0:21:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我是不是也该要保养了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.92,0:21:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,最好的方法就是多做爱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.82,0:21:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,还有就是最好跟老公一起洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.13,0:21:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,洗澡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.13,0:21:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我要出门了\N路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.83,0:21:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,等我一下，载我到车站去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.54,0:21:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,妈要去哪里\N护肤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.84,0:21:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那么老了不需要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.75,0:21:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,爱理，我去跑步
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.17,0:23:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,夏子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.87,0:23:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是去护肤了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.68,0:24:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,爱理
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.98,0:24:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我马上就好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.50,0:24:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,爱理，你在干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.60,0:24:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这样不行
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.83,0:24:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,爱理
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.93,0:25:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.84,0:25:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，真的不行
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.24,0:25:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以，这样不好
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.15,0:25:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我会保守秘密的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.36,0:25:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我搬来之后 看到爸妈的男女情事
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.46,0:25:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,从此我就变得怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.07,0:25:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想试试那么激烈的性爱
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.27,0:25:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,求求爸，就这么一次
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.88,0:25:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,就这么一次
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.59,0:25:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,真的就这么一次
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.70,0:26:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，还是不行，爱理
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.11,0:26:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，我没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.41,0:26:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.90,0:27:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸已经硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.51,0:27:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好硬
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.92,0:28:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸的宝贝好有精神
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.92,0:28:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，这样不行
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.74,0:28:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.63,0:31:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸，舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.23,0:31:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,真的好硬哦
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.54,0:31:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,爱理，你不要这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.65,0:31:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.95,0:32:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,尽管舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.86,0:32:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，爱理
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.39,0:32:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，爱理
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.30,0:32:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,来，穿好
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.30,0:32:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,穿好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.90,0:32:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.52,0:33:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,真的不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.03,0:33:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.53,0:33:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,真的不可以吗\N真的...真的不能放进去
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.94,0:33:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,爸...求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.46,0:33:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.97,0:33:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.68,0:34:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,真的好硬
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.19,0:34:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
