Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.97,0:43:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,爸
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.41,0:44:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.55,0:45:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸，这样好舒服哦
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.88,0:45:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,爸
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.50,0:46:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,真的好舒服哦
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.80,0:46:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.71,0:46:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.81,0:46:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了 糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.22,0:46:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,爸
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.43,0:46:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你舒服吗 我也很舒服哦
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.74,0:46:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒 一直到深处了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.56,0:47:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,爸，我快不行了
