Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.80,0:47:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.82,0:48:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,爸，你顶得太深了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.62,0:48:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我又要去了...舒服
