Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.73,1:16:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,真的好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.43,1:16:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好紧
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.74,1:16:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了 要去了啦
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.35,1:16:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了了
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.95,1:16:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴要坏了...我不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.25,1:16:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸太猛了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.16,1:17:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,很爽吧
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.86,1:17:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,又要去了...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.07,1:17:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,太猛了，我快不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.98,1:17:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,爱理的小穴好紧
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.59,1:17:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,来了，又要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.00,1:17:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.10,1:17:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,来了，真的来了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.80,1:17:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.81,1:17:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.22,1:18:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我快去了 爸我真的不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.22,1:18:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,太猛了
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.84,1:18:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服\N我也好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.15,1:18:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.46,1:18:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.17,1:18:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，我真的不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.28,1:19:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去了...一起去吧 我也要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.48,1:19:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,一起来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.13,1:20:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,真不好意思 只有我这么享受
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.44,1:20:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那很棒啊 可以受邀参加温泉护肤之类的
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.24,1:20:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我的签运一直都不错
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.54,1:20:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们快走吧\N送到车站就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.81,1:20:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,家里就麻烦爱理了 回来再给你带点伴手礼物
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.45,1:20:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,等我啦...真是的
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.82,1:20:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,要小心哦
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.73,1:20:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,今天是我的排卵日
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.15,1:22:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,爱理，今天不行，真的会出事
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.16,1:22:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,真的会出事啦
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.26,1:22:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.47,1:22:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,会出事...今天真的不行
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.64,1:22:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,爸
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.08,1:22:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸跟公平的血型一样吧
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.09,1:22:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚刚跟公平做过爱了
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.76,1:22:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,爱理
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.97,1:22:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道自己在说什么吗
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.50,1:22:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,刚刚一点都不过瘾
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.21,1:23:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我想被爸紧紧地拥入怀中
Dialogue: 0,1:23:05.22,1:23:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,爸
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.89,1:23:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,今天真的不好吧
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.43,1:23:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,爱理...今天不可以
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.80,1:23:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.60,1:23:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,将爸的精液射进我的体内好吗
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.54,1:23:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,爱理...不行...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.63,1:23:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,爱理
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.06,1:24:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,爸
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.57,1:25:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,爸，都这么硬了耶
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.04,1:25:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,今天真的不行吗
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.28,1:25:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.06,1:25:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,爸
Dialogue: 0,1:26:01.76,1:26:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,今天可以吧
Dialogue: 0,1:26:41.70,1:26:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,真的不行吗
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.10,1:26:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,爱理
Dialogue: 0,1:26:52.81,1:26:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,爸
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.45,1:26:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的不要吗
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.22,1:27:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,真的不想 把精液射进我的体内吗
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.23,1:27:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,爸还是不肯答应我吗
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.18,1:28:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,1:28:08.79,1:28:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,其实爸也很想干我的小穴吧
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.63,1:28:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,爱理
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.90,1:28:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,真的不行吗
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.71,1:28:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,爱理
Dialogue: 0,1:28:31.01,1:28:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,今天是排卵日吧
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.12,1:28:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:28:39.72,1:28:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,所以才想要爸爸射在里面
Dialogue: 0,1:28:49.33,1:28:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,爱理
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.54,1:30:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,爸
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.14,1:30:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,爱理
Dialogue: 0,1:31:00.26,1:31:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服哦
Dialogue: 0,1:31:36.30,1:31:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,爱理
Dialogue: 0,1:32:09.63,1:32:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,爸...你闻过头了啦
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.14,1:32:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好香，爱理的小穴真的好香
Dialogue: 0,1:34:32.87,1:34:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴都湿透了
Dialogue: 0,1:35:24.22,1:35:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,爱理你这么容易出水吗
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.03,1:35:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:35:33.53,1:35:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是这里吧
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.94,1:35:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服\N这样对吧
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.44,1:35:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,爱理是这里了吧\N对
Dialogue: 0,1:35:43.44,1:35:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这里吗\N就是那里
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.85,1:35:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,都发出声音来了
Dialogue: 0,1:35:47.65,1:35:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服哦
Dialogue: 0,1:35:59.96,1:36:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那里...不行...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:03.86,1:36:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这样对吧
Dialogue: 0,1:36:10.47,1:36:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了啦
Dialogue: 0,1:36:13.77,1:36:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,爸，要去了...我要去了...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:30.59,1:36:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,爽吧
Dialogue: 0,1:36:33.59,1:36:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服，来了...又来了...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:38.16,1:37:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,爸
Dialogue: 0,1:38:04.89,1:38:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,爸，我帮你舔舔
Dialogue: 0,1:38:16.90,1:38:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:38:22.30,1:38:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我快不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:38:25.61,1:38:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:38:28.31,1:38:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,爸，真的好舒服哦
Dialogue: 0,1:38:35.52,1:38:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,来了，要去了...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:41.52,1:38:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕，要去了...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:57.14,1:39:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,爸，放进去吧
Dialogue: 0,1:39:02.24,1:39:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,放进小穴里吧
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.05,1:39:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,爸，求求你快干我
Dialogue: 0,1:39:16.06,1:39:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,爱理
Dialogue: 0,1:39:19.06,1:39:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么事情我都不负责
Dialogue: 0,1:39:24.46,1:39:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,要射在里面哦
Dialogue: 0,1:39:26.57,1:39:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托你
Dialogue: 0,1:39:33.17,1:39:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要有更舒服的感觉
Dialogue: 0,1:39:53.29,1:39:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,爸...用力...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:56.30,1:39:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,再激烈一点
Dialogue: 0,1:39:59.60,1:40:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,对，用力...用力地
Dialogue: 0,1:40:35.34,1:40:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,爱理
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.64,1:40:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,爸，你顶到最深处了
Dialogue: 0,1:40:42.84,1:40:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,爱理的小穴好紧
Dialogue: 0,1:40:47.95,1:40:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,真的好深
Dialogue: 0,1:40:56.66,1:40:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,1:40:59.66,1:41:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好深
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.67,1:41:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽哦
Dialogue: 0,1:41:28.49,1:41:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,真爽
Dialogue: 0,1:41:32.39,1:41:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不要停...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:35.10,1:41:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,要再来吗
Dialogue: 0,1:41:59.42,1:42:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服\N这样爽吧
Dialogue: 0,1:42:02.42,1:42:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒...就是那里
Dialogue: 0,1:42:05.73,1:42:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒，就是那里了 再用力点干我
Dialogue: 0,1:42:15.04,1:42:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服...好舒服哦...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:23.44,1:42:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,爱理，再干下去我真的要射了
Dialogue: 0,1:42:38.76,1:42:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,真的要射精了
Dialogue: 0,1:42:41.46,1:42:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,射在里面吧
Dialogue: 0,1:42:44.46,1:42:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,射多一点
Dialogue: 0,1:42:54.68,1:42:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,射了...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:45.73,1:43:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,爸射了很多吗
Dialogue: 0,1:43:51.43,1:43:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,再来一次吧
Dialogue: 0,1:43:55.04,1:43:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,爸你真的好厉害
Dialogue: 0,1:44:01.04,1:44:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你也想要吧
Dialogue: 0,1:44:03.14,1:44:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,还要...再射进我的体内
Dialogue: 0,1:44:28.97,1:44:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,真爽
Dialogue: 0,1:44:43.68,1:44:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:44:47.89,1:44:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:44:52.09,1:44:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,爸你真棒
Dialogue: 0,1:45:22.12,1:45:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:45:41.94,1:45:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,爸的肉棒真的好硬 舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:46:34.19,1:46:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,爸再用力一点...激烈一点地干我
Dialogue: 0,1:46:41.40,1:46:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,真的好紧
Dialogue: 0,1:46:47.11,1:46:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:46:50.41,1:46:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,爸...你真的好猛
Dialogue: 0,1:47:06.63,1:47:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,来，屁股转过来这边
Dialogue: 0,1:47:32.15,1:47:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服 真的好舒服哦
Dialogue: 0,1:47:42.36,1:47:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒 干到最深处了
Dialogue: 0,1:47:52.87,1:47:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:47:56.48,1:48:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,来了，要去了...要去了...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:00.68,1:48:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,爸，我不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:48:29.21,1:48:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,爱理，我来帮你爽几下吧
Dialogue: 0,1:48:33.41,1:48:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,1:48:44.22,1:48:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,放进去吧 快...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:05.55,1:49:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,爸
Dialogue: 0,1:49:07.35,1:49:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这样很爽吧\N就是那里
Dialogue: 0,1:49:09.15,1:49:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这样子吗\N不要停
Dialogue: 0,1:49:11.85,1:49:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不要停
Dialogue: 0,1:49:22.96,1:49:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:44.89,1:49:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了，再用力点
Dialogue: 0,1:49:46.99,1:49:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,再用点力吗 我要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:49:48.49,1:49:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,干死你\N好棒，真的好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:49:50.89,1:49:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,太舒服了
Dialogue: 0,1:49:59.00,1:50:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,爸的肉棒真的好硬
Dialogue: 0,1:50:03.80,1:50:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,硬邦邦的肉棒
Dialogue: 0,1:50:05.91,1:50:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,很硬吗
Dialogue: 0,1:50:10.41,1:50:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,千死你这个骚货
Dialogue: 0,1:50:14.62,1:50:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,1:50:16.72,1:50:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,真的好硬
Dialogue: 0,1:50:40.44,1:50:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,爸...真的好爽哦
Dialogue: 0,1:50:47.35,1:50:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:50:50.05,1:50:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,好紧
Dialogue: 0,1:50:52.75,1:50:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我又快忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,1:51:07.17,1:51:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了...要去了...
Dialogue: 0,1:51:09.27,1:51:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,爸，我要去了...
Dialogue: 0,1:51:13.17,1:51:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你快去了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:51:17.98,1:51:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我也快要射了
Dialogue: 0,1:51:22.18,1:51:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,爱理
Dialogue: 0,1:51:23.38,1:51:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这次也要射在里面哦
Dialogue: 0,1:51:26.99,1:51:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,要跟我一起去吗
Dialogue: 0,1:51:32.39,1:51:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,射在里面\N我真的要射了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:51:36.60,1:51:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好的，麻烦爸了
Dialogue: 0,1:51:40.20,1:51:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸，就这样射进去吧
Dialogue: 0,1:51:44.10,1:51:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托你射在小穴里面
Dialogue: 0,1:51:53.71,1:51:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了\N要去了，要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:51:57.32,1:51:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,1:52:06.93,1:52:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴都被我灌满了
Dialogue: 0,1:52:16.84,1:52:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:52:26.15,1:52:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,真的好紧
Dialogue: 0,1:52:32.45,1:52:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧\N要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:52:37.56,1:52:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我也要射了\N射进去吧
Dialogue: 0,1:52:42.96,1:52:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,射在里面吧\N我真的要射了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:52:46.57,1:52:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,就这么射进去吧
Dialogue: 0,1:52:49.57,1:52:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你要求我的哦
Dialogue: 0,1:52:55.58,1:52:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:52:58.88,1:53:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,1:53:06.69,1:53:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我好像要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:53:10.59,1:53:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,爸，你真的太厉害了\N爱理
Dialogue: 0,1:53:17.80,1:53:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:53:25.31,1:53:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,来了...来了...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:28.31,1:53:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:54:19.96,1:54:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,1:54:35.88,1:54:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,1:54:41.88,1:54:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,要再猛一点吗\N要...要...
Dialogue: 0,1:54:45.49,1:54:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,干死你
Dialogue: 0,1:54:54.49,1:54:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我要再射进去了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:54:59.30,1:55:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧\N灌满你的骚穴
Dialogue: 0,1:55:16.72,1:55:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,爽啦
Dialogue: 0,1:55:26.93,1:55:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,真的好紧
Dialogue: 0,1:55:31.43,1:55:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,爱理，我快不行了...
Dialogue: 0,1:55:34.74,1:55:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,射在里面吧
Dialogue: 0,1:55:41.04,1:55:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了...要去了...\N一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,1:55:45.25,1:55:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,爸
Dialogue: 0,1:55:47.05,1:55:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,爸，你干得好爽哦\N要射了
Dialogue: 0,1:55:50.95,1:55:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,射了
Dialogue: 0,1:56:30.59,1:56:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,爱理
Dialogue: 0,1:56:55.82,1:56:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来了\N辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,1:56:58.82,1:57:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,果然还是家里舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:57:01.82,1:57:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我帮妈泡茶
Dialogue: 0,1:57:07.83,1:57:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你们昨天有做爱吗
Dialogue: 0,1:57:15.64,1:57:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这次应该会中吧
Dialogue: 0,1:57:21.34,1:57:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,孙子吗，真的好期待

